longBusinessSummary: Birmingham Sports Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, operates a professional football club in the United Kingdom, the People's Republic of China, Cambodia, and Japan. The company also invests in residential and commercial properties. In addition, it provides management services; medical consultation, and healthcare and wellness referral related services; and money lending services. The company was formerly known as Birmingham International Holdings Limited and changed its name to Birmingham Sports Holdings Limited in May 2017. Birmingham Sports Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2002 and is based in Wong Chuk Hang, Hong Kong.
